    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/b384a4b67cda99c1583811b3f6791e50.avif?t=1656606105\" width=614 height=344 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>嗨！亲爱的玩家你们好，很高兴见到你们！我们是白骑士工作室。</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《灾厄清除系统》是一款二次元风格的、roguelike单人卡牌构建式游戏。</strong></h2><br>不知从何时起，一种名为“灾厄”的未知病毒在宇宙中快速扩散。灾厄会使人发狂，爆发冲突，直到毁灭星球上的一切。与此同时，你作为先驱者降临在了被灾厄侵蚀的世界，本能地受到神秘声音的指引，开始带领女武神清除灾厄，终止灾厄的扩散。同时你也会在完成使命的旅途中经历各种有趣的冒险，逐步找到被选中的原因及事情的真相。<br><br>对于先驱者而言，你的存在就如同神一样，你的指令就如同神的指引，而自己则是神的聆听者与代言人。女武神则是神的仆从，她们将会忠实地执行由先驱者——神的代言人所发出的任何命令，也正是这样的忠诚，女武神们能够完成一个个看似不可能完成的任务。<br>同时灾厄清除的成果越好，你就能得到更多的奖励。<br><br>你将召唤或唤醒强大的女武神来完成任务；<br>你将配置合适的指令来带领她们战斗；<br>你将在奇妙的世界经历各种奇遇，也会遇见越加强大的对手；<br>一切为了清除灾厄！探寻真相！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>美丽强大的女武神</strong></h2>先驱者召唤的强大伙伴，协助清除任务。你有多种途径获得众多的华丽女武神，她们拥有精美的动态立绘和独特的强力技能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/95c284082d9ad54cd5e53c859d1a7864.poster.avif?t=1656606105\" width=158 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/95c284082d9ad54cd5e53c859d1a7864.webm?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/95c284082d9ad54cd5e53c859d1a7864.mp4?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精心打造的小队</strong></h2>你可以自由组建六人小队，试着根据女武神们的不同特性搭配出强大的队伍吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/34f3e4d06a564d7501873a344cfaf5ab.poster.avif?t=1656606105\" width=614 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/34f3e4d06a564d7501873a344cfaf5ab.webm?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/34f3e4d06a564d7501873a344cfaf5ab.mp4?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动态构建的指令（卡牌）</strong></h2>游戏开始时，你会得到一些先驱者指令。随着游戏推进，你可以通过多个途径获得更多的指令。指令可以升级得到更强效果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/659f4dadc0d3a18cec6ed9d80bb6dacc.poster.avif?t=1656606105\" width=614 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/659f4dadc0d3a18cec6ed9d80bb6dacc.webm?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/659f4dadc0d3a18cec6ed9d80bb6dacc.mp4?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精彩绝伦的战斗</strong></h2>先驱者与女武神之间可以互相配合，产生不可思议的力量。请尽情发挥你的想象力，体验充满策略性的精彩战斗！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/95bb1bb6290f157014d2f5cfa58d1c4f.poster.avif?t=1656606105\" width=614 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/95bb1bb6290f157014d2f5cfa58d1c4f.webm?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/95bb1bb6290f157014d2f5cfa58d1c4f.mp4?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>未知的奇遇事件</strong></h2>游戏中设计了数量极多的奇遇事件，你掷出的点数会影响最终的结果。（小心急救大失败）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/9b9034a118bc20563d72e89423c47a04.poster.avif?t=1656606105\" width=614 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/9b9034a118bc20563d72e89423c47a04.webm?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/9b9034a118bc20563d72e89423c47a04.mp4?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelike元素</strong></h2>大量的女武神、指令、事件、怪物使得这个宇宙充满了无穷变数与新意，每次开始都将会是一个新的任务。<br>为了公司的前景，又或者是为了满足个人欲望，好好干吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/265e49de112d065f41f16e9aa3b13d39.poster.avif?t=1656606105\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/265e49de112d065f41f16e9aa3b13d39.webm?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632330/extras/265e49de112d065f41f16e9aa3b13d39.mp4?t=1656606105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
